#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1567
msgid ""
"Stops the function execution and returns the current suspended state to the "
"calling function."
msgstr "停止执行函数，并将当前的挂起状态返回给调用函数。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1569
msgid ""
"From the caller, call :ref:`GDScriptFunctionState.resume "
"<class_GDScriptFunctionState_method_resume>` on the state to resume "
"execution. This invalidates the state. Within the resumed function, "
"``yield()`` returns whatever was passed to the ``resume()`` function call."
msgstr ""
"从调用者处，在该状态下调用 :ref:`GDScriptFunctionState.resume "
"<class_GDScriptFunctionState_method_resume>` 以恢复执行。这会使状态无效。在恢"
"复的函数中，``yield()`` 返回传递给 ``resume()`` 函数调用的内容。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1571
msgid ""
"If passed an object and a signal, the execution is resumed when the object "
"emits the given signal. In this case, ``yield()`` returns the argument "
"passed to ``emit_signal()`` if the signal takes only one argument, or an "
"array containing all the arguments passed to ``emit_signal()`` if the signal "
"takes multiple arguments."
msgstr ""
"如果传递了对象和信号，则在对象发出给定信号时恢复执行。在这种情况下，如果信号"
"仅接受一个参数，则 ``yield()`` 返回传递给 ``emit_signal()`` 的参数；或如果信"
"号采用多个参数，则包含所有传递给 ``emit_signal()`` 的参数的数组。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1573
msgid "You can also use ``yield`` to wait for a function to finish:"
msgstr "您也可以使用 ``yield`` 来等待一个函数完成："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1596
msgid ""
"When yielding on a function, the ``completed`` signal will be emitted "
"automatically when the function returns. It can, therefore, be used as the "
"``signal`` parameter of the ``yield`` method to resume."
msgstr ""
"当正在yeild一个函数时，函数返回时会自动发出 ``completed`` 信号。因此，可以将"
"其用作要恢复的 ``yield`` 方法的 ``signal`` 参数。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_@gdscript.rst:1598
msgid ""
"In order to yield on a function, the resulting function should also return a "
"``GDScriptFunctionState``. Notice ``yield(get_tree(), \"idle_frame\")`` from "
"the above example."
msgstr ""
"为了在一个函数上yield，生成的函数还应该返回一个 ``GDScriptFunctionState``。注"
"意上例中的 ``yield(get_tree(), \"idle_frame\")``。"

